abstract: Baseball Roundup; Cincinnati Reds defeat Washington Nationals, 8-2; other MLB scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The Cincinnati Reds rallied for six runs in the seventh inning on Sunday and beat the visiting Washington Nationals, 8-2.

headline.main: Joey Votto’s Three-Ball Walk Helps Reds Prevail
